Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' for cases that are eventually approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average resolution time for cases involving 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' in cases where a rejection is followed by approval
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Minimum time it takes for a case to be resubmitted after 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' in cases that are eventually approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total resolution time of cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' compared to cases without this activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Average time to resolve a case after 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' compared to the average time to resolve cases without this rejection
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time to 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' from the initial submission
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to the next activity in the process
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Request Payment' in cases that proceed to payment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Minimum resolution time of cases with 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' compared to cases that are directly approved without rejections
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to case closure, distinguishing between cases closed with payment and those closed without payment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and the end of case where activity 'Payment Handled occurs

Name: Total time it takes for a case to be finalized after 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER', comparing cases that require director approval to those that do not
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and the end of case grouped by the last value of org:role
